<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= @oldevent.eventtype.name %> Changed</h1>
    <p>
    Hi <%= @player.first_name %>, <br />
    This is to inform you that the <%= @oldevent.eventtype.name %> has been changed: <br />
    <%= @oldevent.eventtype.name %>: <%= @oldevent.the_date %>, <%= @oldevent.the_time.strftime('%H:%M %P')%> at <%=@oldevent.event_location %> <br /> 
    is now<br />
    <b><%= @event.eventtype.name %>: <%= @event.the_date %>, <%= @event.the_time.strftime('%H:%M %P')%> at <%=@event.event_location %></b>
    <br /> 
    
    More information can be found be checking the schedule <%=link_to "here", @player.team %>
    </p>
    <p>
      This is an automated email. Please do not reply
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
